18 The ability of a defendant to pay court financial obligations may
19 not impact the sentence imposed.
20 2. Defendants with court financial obligations who are found by
21 shall impose any fines, court costs, fees, and assessments
22 authorized by law, subject to the provisions of paragraphs 3 and 4
23 of this subsection and subsection C of this section.
